1
00:00:01,980 --> 00:00:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quick! Get back!</font>

2
00:00:03,320 --> 00:00:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop him!</font>

3
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

4
00:00:07,030 --> 00:00:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pass it!</font>

5
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayase-senpai.</font>

6
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job.</font>

7
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice one.</font>

8
00:00:24,310 --> 00:00:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get back on defense.</font>

9
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me.</font>

10
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

11
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

12
00:00:57,620 --> 00:00:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

13
00:01:01,490 --> 00:01:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a favor to ask you.</font>

14
00:02:37,010 --> 00:02:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an8}<font color="#e7c479">Festival of Offerings</font></b></font></font>

15
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS">Episode 4: A Replica Cries</font></font>

16
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our last day?</font>

17
00:02:45,050 --> 00:02:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's that?</font>

18
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was created so Shuya 
could have his revenge.</font>

19
00:02:52,350 --> 00:02:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Revenge?</font>

20
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm supposed to lure out Hayase and
 beat him up beyond all hope of recovery.</font>

21
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayase will claim Shuya did it,</font>

22
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but at the time of the attack, he'll be 
elsewhere with plenty of witnesses.</font>

23
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he'll have an airtight alibi.</font>

24
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

25
00:03:15,770 --> 00:03:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It all goes down next Monday.</font>

26
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?</font>

27
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because he wants revenge.</font>

28
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why must <i>you</i> do it?</font>

29
00:03:23,950 --> 00:03:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't Sanada-kun beat him up instead?</font>

30
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What Hayase-senpai did 
was absolutely horrible.</font>

31
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was, but...</font>

32
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't Sanada-kun 
beat him up himself?</font>

33
00:03:39,970 --> 00:03:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why must you shoulder that burden?</font>

34
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want to beat anyone up, do you?</font>

35
00:04:01,170 --> 00:04:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hands are so gentle.</font>

36
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They weren't meant to hurt anyone.</font>

37
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here because Shuya needs me.</font>

38
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! You're...</font>

39
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here so we'd meet each other!</font>

40
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here so we could go to the zoo.</font>

41
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we could go to the amusement park.</font>

42
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we could go to an aquarium.
 To a movie theater.</font>

43
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never realized we'd have 
such a packed schedule.</font>

44
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And next year, we'll go see
 the fireworks together!</font>

45
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, I don't care where we go.</i></font>

46
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As long as he's smiling next to me.</i></font>

47
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

48
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to beat him up, either.</font>

49
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

50
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll call Shuya.</font>

51
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14">Shuya Sanada</font></font></font>

52
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="18">Shuya Sanada</font></font></font>

53
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can listen in.</font>

54
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hello?</i></font>

55
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shuya, I'm sorry.</i></font>

56
00:05:16,090 --> 00:05:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go along with your revenge plan.</font>

57
00:05:23,730 --> 00:05:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we hurt Hayase-senpai, 
it'd make us no different from him.</font>

58
00:05:29,170 --> 00:05:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A replica is supposed to follow orders
 from the original.</i></font>

59
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Aki-kun is completely 
rejecting that rule.</i></font>

60
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He crossed that line 
without putting on airs.</i></font>

61
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So you're saying 
I shouldn't have my revenge?</i></font>

62
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm saying there's 
a better way to get revenge.</font>

63
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What way?</i></font>

64
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a real athlete would.</font>

65
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like we could.</font>

66
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

67
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's how you want to do it, 
then go ahead.</font>

68
00:06:07,970 --> 00:06:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10">Shuya Sanada</font></font></font>

69
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8">{\an1}Shuya Sanada</font></font></font>

70
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He gave the okay.</font>

71
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank goodness.</font>

72
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still going down next Monday.</font>

73
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also want you to do something for me.</font>

74
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

75
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can, I want you to be there for me.</font>

76
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I know you're there, 
I don't think I'd lose to anyone.</font>

77
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go to school 
in your place next Monday.</font>

78
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, come inside.</font>

79
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can talk about it.</font>

80
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

81
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That explains everything.</font>

82
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knew Sanada had a replica, too?</font>

83
00:07:07,010 --> 00:07:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Sorry for not telling you sooner.</font>

84
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

85
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually sort of get it.</font>

86
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

87
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for Monday, go ahead. 
We can switch places.</font>

88
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

89
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll need one thing in return.</font>

90
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

91
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask me for anything.</font>

92
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll even get a perfect score 
on the next test.</font>

93
00:07:32,850 --> 00:07:34,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do whatever you want.</font>

94
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to watch, too.</font>

95
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to see Sanada get revenge
 on Hayase-senpai.</font>

96
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11"><font color="#595d69">Suru-Sei Boys' Basketball</font></font></b></font>

97
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Thanks for three awesome years!</font></font></b></font>

98
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Make it to the Inter-High next year!</font></font></b></font>

99
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Thanks a lot!</font></font></b></font>

100
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">You all did great!</font></font></b></font>

101
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8"><font color="#d6d9e4">Today</font></font></b></font>

102
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10"><font color="#6494c6">@Hayase</font></font></b></font></font>

103
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="13"><font color="#595d69">Let's settle it 1 on 1</font></font></b></font>

104
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="52"><font color="#4f92ce">{\an1}@Hayase</font></font></b></font>

105
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="52"><font color="#261d21">{\an1}Let's settle it 1 on 1</font></font></b></font>

106
00:07:59,790 --> 00:08:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll announce the starters for 
the prefectural prelims.</font>

107
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shuya Sanada.</font>

108
00:08:03,970 --> 00:08:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

109
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11"><font color="#595d69">Suru-Sei Boys' Basketball</font></font></b></font>

110
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Thanks for three awesome years!</font></font></b></font>

111
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Make it to the Inter-High next year!</font></font></b></font>

112
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">Thanks a lot!</font></font></b></font>

113
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10"><font color="#595d69">You all did great!</font></font></b></font>

114
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8"><font color="#d6d9e4">Today</font></font></b></font>

115
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10"><font color="#6494c6">@Hayase</font></font></b></font></font>

116
00:08:22,110 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="13"><font color="#595d69">Let's settle it 1 on 1</font></font></b></font>

117
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="65"><font color="#0e1011">You got it</font></font></b></font>

118
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="30"><font color="#5e6d92">Message sent</font></font></b></font>

119
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Hayase-senpai 
really did injure Sanada-kun?</font>

120
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess. But Sanada-kun told the teachers 
he fell down some stairs.</font>

121
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he did?</font>

122
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There. We're all good to go.</font>

123
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

124
00:08:45,430 --> 00:08:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for asking such a weird favor.</font>

125
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't sweat it. 
I'm always happy to oblige.</font>

126
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're here.</font>

127
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

128
00:09:07,570 --> 00:09:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going live.</font>

129
00:09:13,650 --> 00:09:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayase-senpai.</font>

130
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for taking time out to come here.</font>

131
00:09:20,770 --> 00:09:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure you're fully healed?</font>

132
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm able to manage it day-to-day.</font>

133
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to hear it.</font>

134
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even joined 
the literature club, they say.</font>

135
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So here's how it's gonna go.</font>

136
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:44,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I win, you have to apologize.</font>

137
00:09:45,730 --> 00:09:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For breaking my ankle.</font>

138
00:09:47,570 --> 00:09:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? He really did it?</font>

139
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way.</font>

140
00:09:56,930 --> 00:09:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I win?</font>

141
00:09:59,010 --> 00:10:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to break my other leg...</font>

142
00:10:05,330 --> 00:10:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll play one-on-one 
with no time limit.</font>

143
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first to make a basket wins.</font>

144
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll start on defense.</font>

145
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? You sure about that?</font>

146
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, it'll be a fair fight.</font>

147
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready when you are.</font>

148
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the hell? 
Did he just fake getting faked out?</i></font>

149
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my ball now.</font>

150
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Way to go, Sanada-kun.</font>

151
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is getting wild.</font>

152
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your ankle <i>did</i> heal up.</font>

153
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you see it that way.</font>

154
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have my payback, Senpai.</font>

155
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go in.</font>

156
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai, remember what you taught me?</font>

157
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:25,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Playing man-to-man 
is all about your acting chops.</font>

158
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who makes a shot like that?</font>

159
00:12:35,450 --> 00:12:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang.</font>

160
00:12:37,410 --> 00:12:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I win.</font>

161
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know <i>why</i> I didn't squeal on you?</font>

162
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

163
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it for the team.</font>

164
00:12:50,410 --> 00:12:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The prelims were on the line.</font>

165
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't stay quiet for you, Senpai.</font>

166
00:12:58,880 --> 00:12:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai?</font>

167
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was...</font>

168
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just an accident.</font>

169
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sorry it happened.</font>

170
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Nice game.</font>

171
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You rock!</font>

172
00:13:23,490 --> 00:13:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was intense!</font>

173
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get everything?</font>

174
00:13:33,090 --> 00:13:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problemo. I caught every second.</font>

175
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sanada-senpai was amazing.</font>

176
00:13:39,470 --> 00:13:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. He really was!</font>

177
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:47,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'm heading back to class now. 
I haven't eaten lunch yet.</font>

178
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. And thanks again.</font>

179
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't mention it.</font>

180
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm spent.</font>

181
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were incredible.</font>

182
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Score.</font>

183
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="10">{\an1}<font color="#f8f9fb">Group Call</font></font></b></font>

184
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Shuya Sanada</font></font></b></font>

185
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Sunao Aikawa</font></font></b></font>

186
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Aki</font></font></b></font>

187
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Accept</font></font></b></font>

188
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Decline</font></font></b></font>

189
00:14:58,800 --> 00:14:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nice work.</i></font>

190
00:15:01,090 --> 00:15:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

191
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You really beat him.</i></font>

192
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks to me.</i></font>

193
00:15:09,270 --> 00:15:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You did great.</i></font>

194
00:15:10,970 --> 00:15:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

195
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, you know... 
It doesn't even hurt for you.</i></font>

196
00:15:18,950 --> 00:15:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So, yeah, I bet that helped.</i></font>

197
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Bear with me.</font>

198
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yowch!</font>

199
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an1}<font color="#f8f9fb">Group Call</font></font></b></font>

200
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Shuya Sanada</font></font></b></font>

201
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Sunao Aikawa</font></font></b></font>

202
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Aki</font></font></b></font>

203
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Leave</font></font></b></font>

204
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Turn On Video</font></font></b></font>

205
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#474645">Mic</font></font></b></font>

206
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="11">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Speaker</font></font></b></font>

207
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of <i>course</i> it hurts for him!</font>

208
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He played through the pain 
for that entire one-on-one!</font>

209
00:15:43,290 --> 00:15:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hold on. Does that mean 
you feel pain, too?</i></font>

210
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When your head hurts, mine hurts, too.</font>

211
00:15:51,570 --> 00:15:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When your stomach hurts, so does mine.</font>

212
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you've never once mentioned that.</font>

213
00:15:58,130 --> 00:16:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't tell you.</i></font>

214
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't.</font>

215
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want to be useful to you, Sunao.</font>

216
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After all, I'm her replica.</i></font>

217
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whenever I see Sunao lying in bed 
worry-free, I feel relieved.</i></font>

218
00:16:18,250 --> 00:16:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's proof that she still needs me.</i></font>

219
00:16:25,890 --> 00:16:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Aki-kun must also—</font>

220
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we'll leave the call now.</font>

221
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two originals can have a private line.</font>

222
00:16:32,190 --> 00:16:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>H-Hey, wait—</i></font>

223
00:16:35,610 --> 00:16:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Sunao and 
Sanada-kun will talk about.</font>

224
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll bet Aikawa wants to ask Shuya 
how he deals with a replica.</font>

225
00:16:44,770 --> 00:16:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

226
00:16:45,990 --> 00:16:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike you, Shuya has never 
made me disappear.</font>

227
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hasn't?</font>

228
00:16:51,410 --> 00:16:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. I take over for Shuya 
at school and at home.</font>

229
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

230
00:16:58,920 --> 00:17:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he did erase and resummon me, 
I'd probably come back chubby.</font>

231
00:17:03,950 --> 00:17:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shuya's been cooped up 
in his room after all.</font>

232
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Nao.</font>

233
00:17:11,430 --> 00:17:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never played basketball before.</font>

234
00:17:15,330 --> 00:17:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you didn't practice anyway.</font>

235
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanted to show you could win 
purely by using Sanada-kun's skills.</font>

236
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

237
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wasn't even sure that I'd win.</font>

238
00:17:27,490 --> 00:17:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was a nervous wreck.</font>

239
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I made it through 
because you cheered me on.</font>

240
00:17:32,890 --> 00:17:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You heard me?</font>

241
00:17:34,450 --> 00:17:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

242
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said "go in" right at the end there.</font>

243
00:17:41,150 --> 00:17:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that you were awesome,</font>

244
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you shouldn't do this anymore.</font>

245
00:17:45,300 --> 00:17:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to take care of yourself.</font>

246
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. You win.</font>

247
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean it. Never again.</font>

248
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise.</font>

249
00:17:57,290 --> 00:17:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is me, Aikawa.</font>

250
00:17:58,770 --> 00:18:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh, yeah.</i></font>

251
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an1}<font color="#f8f9fb">Group call</font></font></b></font>

252
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="7">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Shuya Sanada</font></font></b></font>

253
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="7">{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Sunao Aikawa</font></font></b></font>

254
00:18:00,860 --> 00:18:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think this is our first time 
speaking to each other.</i></font>

255
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

256
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm still surprised you have a replica.</i></font>

257
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too. I was shocked by yours.</font>

258
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so, I've gotta hand it to him.</i></font>

259
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's supposed to be me, 
but it's like he has what I don't.</i></font>

260
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can definitely relate.</font>

261
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

262
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

263
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for you. You got 
your revenge on Hayase-senpai.</font>

264
00:18:29,730 --> 00:18:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, yeah.</i></font>

265
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="8">{\an1}<font color="#f8f9fb">Group call</font></font></b></font>

266
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Shuya Sanada</font></b></font>

267
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f8f9fb">Sunao Aikawa</font></b></font>

268
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're right. 
It's thanks to everything he's done.</i></font>

269
00:18:35,940 --> 00:18:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of </i>course<i> it hurts for him!</i></font>

270
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He played through the pain 
for that entire one-on-one!</i></font>

271
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

272
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da!</font>

273
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#96909b"><font size="14">Title: <i>Dual x Duet</i>
Ritsuko Hironaka</font></font></font>

274
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At long last, I finally 
finished my first draft.</font>

275
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

276
00:18:53,520 --> 00:18:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice job.</font>

277
00:18:55,530 --> 00:18:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you all very much.</font>

278
00:18:57,690 --> 00:19:00,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I have to do a bunch of revisions.</font>

279
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I pray that Ricchan wins the novel prize.</font>

280
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do it too, Aki-kun.</font>

281
00:19:08,540 --> 00:19:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Uh, right.</font>

282
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

283
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come with you to the station.</font>

284
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what about your bike?</font>

285
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

286
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just have it camp 
overnight at school.</font>

287
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, why not?</font>

288
00:19:32,210 --> 00:19:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it.</font>

289
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can lean on me if you want.</font>

290
00:19:49,130 --> 00:19:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can even rest on my lap.</font>

291
00:20:10,730 --> 00:20:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what's going to happen next.</font>

292
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shuya will probably erase me for good.</font>

293
00:20:19,570 --> 00:20:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think he'll recover eventually.</font>

294
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll get to the point 
where he can go to school himself.</font>

295
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when he does...</font>

296
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He won't need me anymore.</font>

297
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he can't.</font>

298
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that story you mentioned?
 I think it was <i>The Mermaid's Return.</i></font>

299
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet that's pretty much 
what's gonna happen to me.</font>

300
00:20:54,360 --> 00:21:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A six-car local train to Hamamatsu 
will arrive shortly on track 4.</i></font>

301
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:04,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to go to a movie.</font>

302
00:21:06,410 --> 00:21:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about now?</font>

303
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Let's go tomorrow.</font>

304
00:21:14,330 --> 00:21:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Please board the train at spots 
7 through 12 as indicated on the platform.</i></font>

305
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I know I shouldn't make promises.</font>

306
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But still, whatever happens, I'll...</font>

307
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll still...</font>

308
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nao!</font>

309
00:22:17,860 --> 00:22:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="20">Translation: Gad Onyeneho
Timing: Mariana Martinez
Editing: SMR
Quality Control: Riley Dalton
Translation Check: David Saylor</font></b></font>

